"""
pipeline_corpus_teologi.py — RAG v6.5 (CockroachDB)
Mengingest corpus Katolik + Ignatian ke theological_chunks
dan mendaftarkan pointer metadata di ai_knowledge_base.

Target tabel: public.theological_chunks, public.ai_knowledge_base
Embedding model: models/gemini-embedding-2 (768 dim)
"""

